Subject: Re: [T2] Propane tank question, Will this work?????????

We have two 20lb Horizontal tanks that we use for our oven/range. Both ARE
subject to 10 year inspection, and MUST have the new valves to be filled
here in BC. Same regs when we were in California last year.  Been there done
that, went through all of this, still had to get the new valves. Check with
Transport Canada if you are unclear.

Cheers,
Matthew

